 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ueuphorion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Euphorion</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 118<br> <font color=#333333>(8/13/02 9:59:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=314.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Get AGI</span><hr size=1> Hmmmm, not sure...but I think the 107 Agi I got shouldn't be all that bad. and in any case I think I should have gotten at least a messy 1 point increase after thousand(s) of hits.<br>
